properties.jsDoc: External prompt file in files/prompts/ (overrides inline prompts)

properties.jsDoc: Maximum conversation turns (default: 1)

properties.jsDoc: Memory profile: GOLDFISH (2 msgs), MINIMAL (5), FOCUSED (20), FULL (all)

properties.jsDoc: External Python file with Pydantic models (overrides text_format)
